</ul>
<li> A male dog, wolf or fox, as opposed to a bitch (a female dog, wolf or fox).</li>
<li> {derogatory} A dull, unattractive girl or woman.</li>
<ul><li> <em>She’s a real <b>dog</b>.</em></li>
</ul>
<li> {slang} A man.</li>
<ul><li> <em>You lucky <b>dog</b>!</em></li>
</ul>
